column2: select P.objID, P.ra as sdss_ra, P.dec as sdss_dec, W.ra as wise_ra, W.dec as wise_dec, P.psfmag_r, W.w1mpro, P.cModelMag_u, P.cModelMagErr_u, P.cModelMag_g, P.cModelMagErr_g, P.cModelMag_r, P.cModelMagErr_r, P.cModelMag_i, P.cModelMagErr_i, P.cModelMag_z, P.cModelMagErr_z, P.modelMag_u, P.modelMagErr_u, P.modelMag_g, P.modelMagErr_g, P.modelMag_r, P.modelMagErr_r, P.modelMag_i, P.modelMagErr_i, P.modelMag_z, P.modelMagErr_z, P.petroMag_u, P.expAB_u, P.expAB_g, P.expAB_r, P.expAB_i, P.expAB_z into mydb.Table_allwise_a1#sdss from mydb.input_ra_dec_a1# as a CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (a.radeg, a.decdeg, #) AS n JOIN PhotoPrimary AS p ON n.objid = p.objid
